             sworn.</p>
               <p>I lost the thing mentioned in the indictment as my property; they were found upon the prisoner; I had seven shillings and sixpence in my pocket, and eighteen-pence in a trunk; it was all gone.</p>
               <p>(They were produced in court, and deposed to by Smithers.)</p>
